        <p>As an OECM Supplier Partner (Agreement 2025-470), Ontario school boards and colleges can purchase directly from Brant Business Interiors without an open tender or RFP process. We provide a free space layout before you commit &mdash; so the room works on paper before a single piece ships. Most line-item quotes return within one business day.</p>
